## Abstract

- Finally, for constrained networks such as LPWAN, it introduces a
- proxy behavior, where a SCHC Core end-point may anticipate the device
- reaction to incorrect messages.
+ Finally, for constrained networks such as LPWAN, it introduces a
+ proxy behavior, where the SCHC Core Endpoint may anticipate the Device
+ reaction to incorrect messages. Originating these ICMPv6 messages is an
+ IP-layer function co-located with the SCHC Core Endpoint and is outside
+ the SCHC compression/decompression model.

